<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٠٨٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1619">حَمَّادٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1041">ثَابِتٍ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2789">وَشُعَيْبِ بْنِ الْحَبْحَابِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ،</a> <span class="c2">«أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> أَعْتَقَ صَفِيَّةَ وَجَعَلَ عِتْقَهَا صَدَاقَهَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>